HEADWORD: Kipe
<hw>Kipe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OE. <ets>kipen</ets>
to catch, Icel. <ets>kippa</ets> to pull, snatch. Cf.
<er>Kipper</er>.]</ety> <def>An osier basket used for catching
fish.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
